and my brother-in-law Terry.

202
00:09:48,254 --> 00:09:50,974
And the combination
is not known to any human...

203
00:09:51,048 --> 00:09:52,468
Uh, what the...?

204
00:09:52,550 --> 00:09:54,260
"Schlitz plus water."

205
00:09:54,343 --> 00:09:57,183
