and became civilized?

218
00:10:24,665 --> 00:10:25,825
No.

219
00:10:25,916 --> 00:10:28,336
So he could grow hops
and make beer.

220
00:10:28,419 --> 00:10:30,169
-It's true.
-Oh.

221
00:10:30,254 --> 00:10:32,844
